title: Favorite 3rd Party Tools
eventShortDescription: ​In the big world of Microsoft it's easy to forget that there are a lot of other smart cookies out there building great programs and utilities. You could spend hours scouring the net for the latest .exe or you could save time and let Adam show you the best new tools around. These tools will help you write code quicker, upsize faster than ever before, and build better ASP.NET 4.6.1 pages, along with dozens of other useful tricks that will no doubt save you time if you're developing in Windows Forms, ASP.NET, SQL Server or Access.​
